    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>butternut squash cubes</strong> to a baking tray (or two!) with your <strong>dried oregano </strong>and <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>, then give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for an initial 10-12 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/butternut-squash-cubes-on-tray-1717062197462-x200.jpg",
