            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your <strong>bulgur wheat</strong> to a pot with plenty of<strong> boiled water</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 7-9 min or until tender with a slight bite</p><p>Once cooked, drain and return to the pot</p><p>Wash your <strong>shredded kale</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-3-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-3-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-3-x1000.jpg",
