          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the butternut squash and broccoli are done, add your<strong> pumpkin seeds</strong> to the tray[s] and return to the oven for a further 2-3 min or until the seeds are toasted</p><p>Tip: Watch them like a hawk to make sure they don’t burn!</p><p>Whilst the seeds are toasting, add the <strong>cooked bulgur wheat</strong> to the pan with the softened kale, lentils and onion and stir it all together – these are your <strong>grains</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/RC2228Step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted butternut squash </strong>and<strong> Tenderstem broccoli</strong> over the <strong>grains</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>miso dressing</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>toasted pumpkin seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
